title: MIKEOL'S GLOBAL MANHUNT SCI-FI BOOK IDEAS.docx
description: This is a list of ideas for a controversial sci-fi book and e book. Please feel free to flesh it out into a trilogy or even a solo book. Also feel free to change character names. But if you use any or all of my ideas and the book gets published in print or digital format please give me credit for being the one you got the ideas from whether or not you change anything
